lead_paragraph: Never mind the potential for name fatigue. Former U.S. President George W. Bush likes the idea of a 2016 presidential matchup between his Republican brother Jeb Bush and Democrat Hillary Clinton.

headline.main: George W. Bush Likes Idea of Jeb Bush vs Hillary Clinton in 2016
